{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BQFMooGLgfTbyEnvRzD9nN","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# src/lib — Shared Libraries\n     2→\n     3→Pure library modules consumed by CLI commands (`src/commands/`) and by each other. No CLI entry points, no side effects on import.\n     4→\n     5→## State & Output\n     6→\n     7→| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n     8→|------|---------|-------------|\n     9→| state.ts | YAML front-matter state persistence in `.claude/codeharness.local.md` | `readState`, `writeState`, `readStateWithBody`, `getStatePath`, `HarnessState` |\n    10→| output.ts | Structured `[OK]/[FAIL]/[WARN]/[INFO]` CLI output with JSON mode | `ok`, `fail`, `warn`, `info`, `jsonOutput` |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013rWcam9ZLGWy8y97T6yhWS","session_id":"790cd04c-5c91-45bb-998d-78a56b65af9a","uuid":"0903c281-aa97-4eba-ba1a-212a324da8a8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T23:18:00.477Z"}
